reviews.text: Horrible service!!! And the food also is so bad ,  especially pasta. Never come again

Nice and reasonably cosy environment. Convenient to find as it is just next to the escalator and information centre. Very good quiche, soup and salad. Quite expensive but worth paying that for its quality.
Excellent french style bakery. Just crowed as many places in HK but come early for breakfast and you will enjoy good pastries and excellent coffee in almost empty place.
Good salads and sandwiches. Light western  options. Cool decoration.

0/5 Customer service was absolutely appalling...
The process of ordering was confusing as one side was for hot meals and the other side was for desserts, however there were no signs. So I had to make 2 separate orders... Don't understand how these businesses can function with the poor management. On top of that we had no cutlery... Again, poor customer service. 
Food was average. Pizza wasn't fresh. Pretty sure it was microwaved. Peach tart was dry and rubbery. Would never come here again.

reviews.text:
Nice mall; cool place to be.  Lots of dining options, aside from the usual shopping attractions of the multi-level center.

The series of escalators to the upper floors provide an airy space in the middle of the building.  There is an express escalator straight to the lobby of the offices and hotel, bypassing most of the shopping floors.
Langham Place is awesome shopping place. Wonderful design and place. Outstanding shopping mall. I like it. I am satisfied this Google map.

Langham place is the best ever place i have ever visited. People there are very humble with each other and with all the visitors. Amazing place.
Langham Mall is Beautiful shopping mall. Its available all grosery on it. Wonderful shopping mall around the world. I love this place.

reviews.text: 最近愛上吃沙律菜，知道朗豪坊有這間餐廳，聚會前來一個輕食撐枱腳，這裏展示的沙律和甜品都好吸睛👀，下午茶時段人流不算多，好容易就搵到位，自選沙律及蛋餅套餐$80，可以自選三款沙律，我哋揀咗蔬菜伊甸園、地中海小米、雞肉貝殼粉、紅菜頭薯仔豆角，蛋餅選擇了藍莓芝士味，沙律都好新鮮份量也足夠，之後再加多個甘筍蛋糕，感覺健康飽足，除了沙律和甜品，還有多款麵包、意粉、Pizza、雪糕、咖啡特飲等等，選擇都算多元化，下次再來試其他甜品。同場加映漫畫大師手塚治虫誕生90周年展。

我係佢嘅忠實支持者🥰😅😋👍
乜嘢都好食, 真係冇得輸. 
現在我開始減肥, 都要幫襯佢😅

假日早上沒有太多顧客，可以慢慢進餐。
職員有禮，食物質素也不錯。
考完試夜了, 唔想食太多又想食得健康啲, 所以嚟咗呢間餐廳。點了個四款沙津, 食材很新鮮, 味道很清新醒胃, 喺悶熱的春天裡面帶來點清新!
无意中经过想饮杯咖啡，但地面已冇位，上楼上则发现原来有一个装修得这么美丽堂皇的地方。很幸运地坐到露台位置，一边叹咖啡，一边享受微风和阳光
